HEADWORD: Scenography
<hw>Sce*nog"ra*phy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>scaenographia</ets>, Gr. <?/; <?/ scene, stage +
<grk>gra`fein</grk> to write: cf. F.
